Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.19,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去成为真正的救世主的身边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到传说的救世主身边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.94,0:03:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一话\N救世主是小学四年级生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,起身了,又要迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡 我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要穿滚轴鞋上学啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快迟到的话就要穿这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个穿过龙神池便到学校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是聪明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神池内住了条很可怕的龙会把坏孩子吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.01,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事一点也不可怕\N我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,这样的东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神大人,我明天会早起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会和妈妈斗嘴,还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会穿上鞋上学\N还有…不会吃剩萝葡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上垒!上垒!出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.15,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己觉得有型的东西\N可爱的东西,什么都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.30,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美,你要做什么?\N我家的芝罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你家的猫吗?很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡你要做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人…我要造机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美 我也要做机械人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瞬也是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要跟我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不要跟我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我先说要造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,那来比\N谁的机械人造得有型吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,不过对你来说\N也是多此一举罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.11,0:06:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有型 真厉害呢\N瞬果然很厉害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.09,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以碰的,好了\N你们借开吧,由美,请看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒呢,你真厉害,瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.52,0:07:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我真是太高兴了\N渡,你也快给我们看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.99,0:07:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想看我的吗?瞬\N那你便看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次的比试是我胜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N那也算是机械人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样奇怪吗?\N虽然和我想像的有点出入…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉?这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确把这个放在龙神池的祠上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱 你觉得是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里?哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?过去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚的话这个也是很有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美\N我和瞬的机械人哪个较有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡胜出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.39,0:08:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神池的龙,我已不怕你了\N因为我有很强的帮手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出来的话便出来看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不替你取个名字不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.76,0:08:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…神…丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了\N你的名字便是龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,起床了,起床啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是… 战部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见龙了吧?\N看…看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.27,0:10:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆,这孩子便是传说中的救世主吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说他可以\N令创界山的七色彩虹苏醒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他会把这条麾沙村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从古怪的天气的侵袭中解放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.91,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令村园里再一次充满一片翠绿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相传每当创界山有危机时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.94,0:11:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救它的人便会从天而降\N他的名字便是渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会与龙神一起把邪恶打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个救世主现在在这里出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.66,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是救世主?\N救世主是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起学校的风纪更伟大吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要拯救这个世界的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N把救世主大人带往神祠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么?我要回家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?很像龙神池呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为创界山的彩虹失去了色彩的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神池的水也干了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是到了未来\N或是过去的世界了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!说起来这种事\N我好像在哪里听过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.96,0:12:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是时间停止…不\N时间加速…不是,时间故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在乱说什么?跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?石浮在空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是创界山的碎片\N渡,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们麾沙村\N代代相传的战士的装束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿上它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以穿吗?我一直很想要那样的滚轴鞋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚轴鞋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出场姿势已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,那座便是创界山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.06,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!很巨大的山呢,奇怪了\N有一条没有颜色的彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人见过他的真面目的\N邪恶大王多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但支配了和平的创界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.29,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还令七色彩虹变成了白色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此这条麾沙村\N也变得异常起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.27,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是要登上创界山\N和多恶达作战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像做梦一样的事呢\N不过没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来干\N不帮助有困难的人不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是一段很艰苦的旅程啊\N你有心理准备了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车也会害怕的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是救护车,是救世主啊\N你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.31,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是问你名字\N你竟然取笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?你不可向忍部一族\N第13代首领出手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首…首领?他说首领…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子是忍部一族的头目啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头目?你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,我是头目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.08,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹啊\N有彩虹从创界山那边来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.92,0:14:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了 有人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的家伙终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.14,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麾沙村的人听着\N我是创界山伟大的支配者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.91,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多恶达大人的七人众的\N其中一人,第一界层的波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古路治大人的左右手\N舒华新力加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很长的自我介绍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.49,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了得到了创界山\N附近的村落也要全部支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.45,0:15:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多恶达大人的命令\N不听命令的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便会有可怕的遭遇\N你们立即发誓效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.05,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?真是傲慢的小孩\N你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.43,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车,渡\N救护车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是救世主,不是救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?我是救世主,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫救世主真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话,让这部战斗\N猩猩的一击令你们清醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.95,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位,这里交给渡\N我们回村吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于来了,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.43,0:16:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,用剑啊\N使用勇者之剑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.09,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔出来了 好!来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一点也不强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.97,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?\N因为是传说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.96,0:16:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真卑鄙,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,怎样啊?救世主\N火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.49,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法 火炎之术,小心火警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了说,那万能鞋\N拍一下的话便会有轮出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拍一次便会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事应该早说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我给你送命的一发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,没子弹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.95,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!小子,你在那里不要动\N绝对不要动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是这样上弹\N战斗猩猩便是无敌的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎办好?\N怎样和那巨大的家伙战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.90,0:17:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龙神丸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.70,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,把勇者之剑\N向着天空呼叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…龙神丸在和我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点,渡\N我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.73,0:18:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个便是传说中的龙神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了?\N那家伙…这不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龙啊\N又到了一个奇怪的世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧,渡,这里是龙神丸\N也就是我的体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,抓住龙的双角吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,现在起我和你一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.84,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会照你的意思行动\N便可以战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我什么也看不见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,去吧,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不抓紧的话会掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为可以胜过我\N舒华新力加的力量吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸有无敌的正义力量\N不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压下去,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.59,0:20:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话便用炮收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,用剑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像已经知道了\N登龙剑的使用方法了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸的剑是叫登龙剑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了,渡!\N死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没弹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向多恶达大人\N报告这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.02,0:21:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你要和龙神丸一起\N拯救创界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.40,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从多恶达的魔爪中救出众神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把彩虹\N恢复七色给你看,等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.86,0:21:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先到第一界层的东方\N多高山上的双龙岩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那处有颗\N拥有不可思议力量的珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.59,0:21:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那得到手的话\N一定可以帮助你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.00,0:21:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了,多高山的双龙岩\N去吧,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.37,0:22:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊


